        <time datetime="@DateTime.Now.ToString()">
            Last updated on @DateTime.Now.ToString("D")
        </time>

        <p>
            This Privacy Policy ("Policy") describes the policies and procedures on the collection, use, disclosure and protection of your information when you use our website located at masterfood.com, or Master Food Private Limited ("Master Food", "Company", "we", "us" and "our"),  a private company established under the laws of India.
        </p>

        <p>
            The terms "you" and "your" refer to the user of the Master Food Platform. The term "Services" refers to any services offered by Master Food whether on the Master Food Platform or otherwise.
        </p>

        <p>
            Please read this Policy before using the Master Food Platform or submitting any personal information to Master Food. This Policy is a part of and incorporated within, and is to be read along with, the Terms of Use.
        </p>

        <h4>Your Consent</h4>

        <p>By using the Master Food Platform and the Services, you agree and consent to the collection, transfer, use, storage, disclosure and sharing of your information as described and collected by us in accordance with this Policy.  If you do not agree with the Policy, please do not use or access the Master Food Platform.</p>


